channel.title: Problem?
channel.description:
Okay, I had a server with over 2k character files made. Anyone with common sense would realize my server worked before. Well, my friend logged into my no-ip before, and when he logged out, it let me use my no-ip on my PC. Now, he logged on for a 2nd time, and now for some reason it doesn't let people connect anymore. I verify that he's logged out. I've changed my no-ip password, also. Does anybody know why it doesn't let anyone connect anymore?
Firewall is off. ISP is Qwest. And I have 2wire wireless internet.
Please respond ASAP.
